\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Sostituendo si ha 
\begin_inset Formula $e^{at_{\varepsilon}}x_{0}=x_{0}\varepsilon\rightarrow e^{at_{\varepsilon}}=\varepsilon\rightarrow t\varepsilon=\dfrac{1}{\left|a\right|}\left|\ln\left(\varepsilon\right)\right|$
\end_inset

